# Best Practices Template
# Guidelines for using this skill effectively.
# See: https://docs.wikilabs.ai/skill-schema-reference
- Verify all detections before acting
- Ask for confirmation before destructive actions
- Document any manual steps taken
- Cross-reference multiple evidence sources
- Keep confidence scores above 0.7 for critical decisions
- Log all actions for auditability
- Review known issues before proceeding
- Always validate changes in non-production first